<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Booking Confirmation</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f9;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .container {
      width: 90%;
      max-width: 800px;
      margin: 50px auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    }
    h1 {
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 20px;
      color: #333;
    }
    p {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 1.2em;
      color: #555;
    }
    .thank-you-message {
      color: #27ae60;
      font-size: 1.5em;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Booking Confirmed!</h1>
    <p class="thank-you-message">Thank you, <%= customerName %>! Your booking has been successfully received. We will get back to you soon with the booking details for your hotel.</p>
    <p>If you need any further assistance, feel free to contact us.</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
